2294 Emergency clause. In view of the emergency cited in the preamble, this legislation
3205 takes effect when approved.
31 SUMMARY
3322 This bill provides funding for 4 Maine State Trooper positions and related All Other to
3333 conduct rural patrols in Washington County.
